# Generated splat cloud (~5MB) built from a 3DGS .ply by scripts/model-to-points.mjs.
# Kept out of git history; the hero falls back to mahjong-points.bin if absent.
# Regenerate:
#   node scripts/model-to-points.mjs <capture.ply> public/models/mahjong-points.bin 150000 --up z
# When the real product capture lands, decide deliberately: `git add -f` it, use
# Git LFS, or fetch it from asset storage at deploy time.
/public/models/*-splats.bin
